<p>Hello there. You've reached the personal site of Simon Mullis.</p>
<div class="section" id="personal">
<h1>Personal</h1>
<p>I'm over 30, married to Anna, and we live in Amsterdam in the Netherlands.  I'm originally from Oxford in the UK.  We have a daughter and a son, Phoebe and Miles.
When I'm not working, playing with technology, I love to play the bass guitar (I've been playing for around 21 years now), and cook (Nom nom nom...).</p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="professional">
<h1>Professional</h1>
<p>I attended the <a class="reference external" href="http://www.sussex.ac.uk/">University of Sussex</a> in Brighton, England and received a BSc in Chemistry; it was at this point
I realised I never, ever wanted to see a test-tube or use a bunsen-burner again and gave up on that,
moving into IT as a career at around the same time this Internet thing started becoming reasonably well known in popular
culture ('95 / '96-ish).</p>
<p>The internet found me in 1994, and <a class="reference external" href="http://groups.google.nl/group/comp.sys.ibm.pc.misc/browse_thread/thread/21584cbb7b6f0abf?hl=en">here is my first ever post</a> (back when the World-Wide-Web was considered &quot;new-fangled&quot;,
<a class="reference external" href="http://www.instinct.org/elm/">elm</a> was my mail client and <a class="reference external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gopher_(protocol)">Gopher</a> was cutting edge.)</p>
<p>Since then, I've worked for a number of technology startups in various pre-sales and post-sales
roles: Sales Engineer, Developer, Systems Admin, Consultant (in no particular order).
Since mid-2006, I've been working for <a class="reference external" href="http://www.juniper.net/">Juniper Networks</a>  initially working with the
<a class="reference external" href="http://www.juniper.net/products_and_services/application_acceleration/data_center_acceleration/dx_application_acceleration/index.html">Layer 7 load balancers</a> and now focussing on the <a class="reference external" href="http://www.juniper.net/products_and_services/application_acceleration/wan_acceleration/wxc_application_acceleration/index.html">WAN Acceleration</a> products.</p>
<p>My professional profile can be viewed on <a class="reference external" href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/smullis">Linked In</a></p>
<p>If you're really interested then you can read how this site works <a class="reference external" href="/colophon/">here</a>.</p>
